20:18.875 --> 20:20.875
-[Gerry]: What am I gonna do
with all these oranges?

20:29.208 --> 20:33.041
-Robert has a play?
-Yeah, you should
check that out.

20:33.083 --> 20:35.083
-Really?
-Yeah, there's nudity.

20:35.125 --> 20:37.500
-What? Really?
-Yeah.

20:37.542 --> 20:39.583
-Well then I will.

20:42.750 --> 20:46.083
[♪ Music]
-[Robert]: ...Same with you,
Miss-ter Trudy Dwyer.

20:46.125 --> 20:49.709
It's time for you people
to see who I really am.

20:49.750 --> 20:51.917
Simon, drumroll please.

20:53.542 --> 20:58.041
[♪ Drumroll]

20:58.083 --> 21:01.625
-I'm sick and tired of people
not seeing the real me.

21:01.667 --> 21:04.250
That's why I've decided to...

21:04.291 --> 21:06.375
Drop all of my walls.

21:09.709 --> 21:12.000
-[Gerry]: Oh...
-[Simon claps]
-[Gerry]: Nope, nope, nope.

21:12.041 --> 21:14.709
-[Bill]: That's the nudity?
-[Gerry]: What are you doing
here?

21:14.750 --> 21:17.917
-[Simon claps alone]: Bravo!

